title: Covered area form of the normal field
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Let $$f\colon M \to \R^3$$ be a parametrized surface with unit normal $$N$$ and Gaussian curvature $$K.$$ Then the covered area form of $$N$$ is $$K {\det}_f.$$